## Detailed Findings

### 🔴 BUG 1 — Dashboard Pillars All Show 0
**Screen:** Home / Dashboard  
**Severity:** High  
**Description:** All three pillar score cards (Nutrition, Fitness, Habits) show `0` even when there is a logged meal for today and a completed habit.

![Dashboard](file:///C:/Users/samcu/.gemini/antigravity/brain/38b94ad7-f8e8-4f63-90ea-fbeb0ca423ce/dashboard_home_1773152279004.png)

**Likely cause:** Dashboard pillar scores may be calculating from a different date range, or the streak/progress query is not matching the user's timezone. The "Let's Go" splash also appears — suggesting the onboarding state may be presenting before real data loads.

---

### 🔴 BUG 2 — Fitness Trends Shows 0 Workouts Despite Swimming Workout Logged
**Screen:** Fitness > Trends (7 Days and 28 Days)  
**Severity:** High  
**Description:** Both 7-day and 28-day views show `0 WORKOUTS` and `0 BURNED`. The consistency grid is entirely empty. This was supposed to be fixed, but the swimming workout logged yesterday is still not appearing.

![Fitness Trends 7d](file:///C:/Users/samcu/.gemini/antigravity/brain/38b94ad7-f8e8-4f63-90ea-fbeb0ca423ce/.system_generated/click_feedback/click_feedback_1773152503028.png)
![Fitness Trends 28d](file:///C:/Users/samcu/.gemini/antigravity/brain/38b94ad7-f8e8-4f63-90ea-fbeb0ca423ce/.system_generated/click_feedback/click_feedback_1773152516814.png)

**Likely cause:** The timezone offset fix in [FitnessTrends.tsx](file:///c:/Users/samcu/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/trak/src/app/fitness/FitnessTrends.tsx) may still be off by a day. The workout was logged at a time that shifts to a different UTC date. Worth checking the `workout_date` stored value in Supabase vs the local date.

---

### 🟡 BUG 3 — Sam Curtis Appears Twice on Leaderboard
**Screen:** Squads > Leaderboard  
**Severity:** Medium  
**Description:** On the "Curtis crew" squad, **Sam Curtis appears at both #2 (66 pts) and #4 (5 pts)**. This suggests two separate user IDs for Sam Curtis are being aggregated separately, or a duplicate squad membership record exists.

![Leaderboard](file:///C:/Users/samcu/.gemini/antigravity/brain/38b94ad7-f8e8-4f63-90ea-fbeb0ca423ce/.system_generated/click_feedback/click_feedback_1773152593927.png)

**Likely cause:** Two distinct user accounts may share the display name "Sam Curtis," or a user has been added to the squad twice under different user IDs. Check `squad_members` table for duplicate `user_id` entries.

---

### 🟡 BUG 4 — Habit Streak Showing 0 Days for Multivitamin
**Screen:** Habits > Today  
**Severity:** Medium  
**Description:** The Multivitamin habit shows `0 DAYS` streak badge even though it should have a streak if previously completed. Creatine correctly shows `🔥 1 DAY`.

![Habits](file:///C:/Users/samcu/.gemini/antigravity/brain/38b94ad7-f8e8-4f63-90ea-fbeb0ca423ce/.system_generated/click_feedback/click_feedback_1773152558539.png)

**Likely cause:** The Multivitamin habit may have been added as a default habit but never completed before today, so streak = 0 is technically correct. However the `0 DAYS` badge is visually misleading — it may be better to hide it when 0.

