## General UX Observations

- **Login:** Only Google OAuth is offered — no email/password option visible. This is the intended design but worth confirming newer users don't expect an email flow.
- **Dashboard splash screen:** "Let's Go" button and the "Consistent Action" motivational screen may feel like a splash delay before real content. Consider auto-dismissing after a timeout if the user has used the app before.
- **Fitness Today "No workouts logged yet today"** — correct empty state, looks clean.
- **Squads multi-squad support** — 3 squads visible (Curtis crew, test, Curtis crew) — the double "Curtis crew" tab is a bit confusing UX-wise.
